title: Philippines Capacity Utilization
description: Capacity Utilization in Philippines increased to 71.52 percent in September from 71.38 percent in August of 2022. Capacity Utilization in Philippines averaged 79.90 percent from 1999 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 84.55 percent in February of 2020 and a record low of 46.15 percent in January of 2021. This page provides - Philippines Capacity Utilization - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Philippine Statistics Authority
